erned with the complementarity of individual and collective perspectivesethnos and anthropos, the intrapsychic and the intersubjective.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 4aPhilosophy. 4aReligious Studies. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / General.2bisacsh  aexistential anthropology, founder of existential anthropology, Michael Jackson anthropology, philosophical anthropology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311075183308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Comm 2023 Englishz978311131910008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Communication 2023z9783111318141oZDB-23-SEW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150176850740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501768507423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501768507/original  a978-3-11-075183-3  Cornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-131910-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Comm 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-SEWb2023